text: Wu Qian (, born July 7, 1994) is a Chinese professional basketball player who plays for the Zhejiang Golden Bulls of the Chinese Basketball Association.Han, trio of guards stand out against South Africa, Fu Yu (China Plus), 20 June 2017. Accessed 17 February 2018.
